long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wonderfeed is an RSS reader for the new tab homepage. Once you add to chrome, Wonderfeed will replace your default new tab and present you the latest news when opening a new tab. Wonderfeed is all about speed and efficiency, collecting all your favorite news sources in one convenient feed.
Users can create their own reading list and keep articles for later reads.
